      <title>中国忧虑刺激铁矿石溃败，铁矿石跌破 100 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/iron-ore-extends-slump-below-100-as-china-concerns-spur-rout</link>
